Job Description:
Licensed Part-Time Family Therapist / Substance Abuse Facility
We are looking to hire an energetic and motivated substance abuse and dual diagnosis Licensed Family Therapist.
Responsibilities include:
Facilitating family therapy using Solution-Focused Therapy (SFT), Motivational Interviewing (MI), Dialectical Behavioral Therapy (DBT), Trauma-Informed Care, and Cognitive-Behavioral Therapy (CBT);
Monitoring client progress and making changes to the therapeutic approach and best practice evidenced-based interventions based on client response to treatment;
Utilizing knowledge of a variety of therapeutic models and theories to understand and plan intervention strategies for a variety of clients;

